page.title: 20CREDITS(cont)& CONCLUSION
page.content: {LOCAL PEOPLE WHO HELPED cont. Mr&Mrs.Fowler,Mrs.Weston,Mrs.Brazier (E.E.S.),Mr&Mrs.Sachs,Mrs.Renton,Mr.& Mrs.Field,Mr.Taylor,Mr.Deal,Mr.A&D McMoreland,Mrs&Mr.Knight,Mr.Lowe,Mrs. Pratt,Mr.McLauglan,Mrs Williams. {MY THOUGHTS ON DOMESDAY by JANE. I think I got an awful lot out of the Domesday Project.We are lucky to be doing it because we are going to be the only Form Six in the school for nine hundred years involved in a Domesday Project.It will be interesting for people in the future to see how we lived.
